      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Ages 18-65

          -  Will undergo bariatric surgery for treatment of obesity in Syracuse NY

          -  Willingness to participate

        Exclusion Criteria:

